# Discriminated Union Mixed Unit and allOf Test

Test fixture for internally tagged discriminated union where the "unspecified"
variant is a plain object with only the discriminator field, while other variants
use allOf to merge a $ref with a discriminator object.

This pattern is generated by serde's `#[serde(tag = "kind")]` when one variant
is a unit variant (no fields) and others carry data from referenced schemas.


Version: `1.0.0`

